ComicInfo.Summary: Shannon Davenport must die before the stroke of midnight at the hands of the Dark Lord. Otherwise, as the chosen one, she will become the new Dark Queen. It is up to Rathnar, the Slayer, to prevent the Dark Lord from succeeding. In his heart, he believes that Shannon will keep the forces of the Dark Realm in check once she inherits her powers. But what if he's wrong? What if she uses her powers to subjugate rather than protect mankind?
